legacy.full_text:
President Xi Jinping said #China will launch 3 proposals:
1⃣Initiative on Supporting Africa’s Industrialization.
2⃣Plan on Supporting Africa’s Agricultural Modernization.
3⃣ Plan for China-Africa Cooperation on Talent Development.
